title: Assassin's Creed Mirage Launch Celebration Gameplay Showcase
description:
Join Chris Watters and Youssef Maguid from the Ubisoft News team as they show off some gameplay from Assassin's Creed Mirage before the game launches on 10/5. We get to see exploration of various parts of Baghdad, missions, combat, and more.

#assassinscreed #mirage #gaming

title: Call of Duty Next Showcase Livestream | Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III, Call of Duty: Warzone
description:
Tune in for Call of Duty Next for the latest reveals and details on upcoming Call of Duty games including live gameplay of Modern Warfare II, Zombies, Warzone and Warzone Mobile.

#callofduty #modernwarfare3

title: MIX Poznan Game Arena Online Showcase
description: The MIX is partnering with the Poznan Game Arena team for an online showcase celebrating developers and games. Poznan Game Arena is the largest show of its kind for Central and Eastern Europe, soon approaching its 20th year.

title: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Official Multiplayer Trailer
description:
World Premiere of the #MW3 Multiplayer Trailer.

16 iconic maps modernized for fast-paced combat.

Tune into #CODNext on October 5 for the premiere of live Multiplayer gameplay!

title: Marvel's Spider-Man 2 Be Greater Together Official Trailer
description:
The Spider-Men are back, Peter Parker and Miles Morales, return for an exciting new adventure in the Marvel’s Spider-Man 2. Equipped with Miles’ new bioelectric venom power and Peter’s Spider-Arms, the Spider-Men face the ultimate test of strength inside and outside the mask as they fight to save the city, each other and the ones they love, from the monstrous Venom. 

Marvel’s Spider-Man 2 launches October 20, 2023.
